{\up A}{\footnote\pard\plain{\up A} a-reversi-overview}
\pard\sb115\sa35\sl-235\li115\ri125 \f1\b\fs18 Reversi overview\plain\f1\fs18
\par
\pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \plain\f1\fs18 Reversi is a board game in which you and the computer take turns placing pieces. You use red pieces; the computer uses blue pieces.
\par
\pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \plain\f1\fs18 A move must outflank at least one opposing piece. Outflanked pieces are flipped to your color, and the side with more pieces at the end wins.
\par
