\pard\sb115\sa35\sl-235\li115\ri125 \f1\b\fs18 Rules\plain\f1\fs18
\par
\pard\sb75\sl-235\li115\ri125 \plain\f1\fs18 Reversi uses one set of rules for moving, flipping pieces, passing, and scoring.
\par
\pard\sb115\sa35\sl-235\li115\ri125 \f1\b\fs18 Rules summary\plain\f1\fs18
\par
